          %p
            Just now i finished my Bachelor in Computer Enginering, and looking forward to do masters in data mining.
          %p
            Currently i work for 
            %a{:href => "http://www.bakedweb.net"} Bakedweb,
            a Design and Web Development shop based in Downtown Miami, Fl. When im not doing that, i read a lot about programming, hangout why my girl or try to do some blogging.

            if you want to hear more about me, 
            %span.line-throught
              can't even imagine why
            check my
            %a{:href => "http://www.twitter.com/odelaguila"} Twitter

